## 📁 ARCHIVE SETUP

At project start:
1. Create `docs/archive/` directory
2. Create `completed_tasks.md` with only this header:
   ```markdown
   # Completed Tasks
   ```
3. Don't add placeholder text like "No tasks completed yet"

