For each completed task, use this exact format:

```markdown
## Task: [Task Name] (v1.0)
Last Updated: YYYY-MM-DD

### Implementation Results
[What was implemented]

### Completed Testing
[How it was tested]

### Lessons Learned
[Key insights gained]

